snippet.title: Uru - Ages Beyond Myst Trailer
snippet.description: Trailer for Cyan Worlds' 2003 PC adventure game Uru: Ages Beyond Myst, with music by Tim Larkin. Uru takes place in the modern era and uses an avatar system with 3rd-person perspective. The puzzles are challenging, but Uru is my least favorite game in the series.
